name: "What Should I Do?" by Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
description: [Gel pen on notebook page with digital embellishments and color.] This is a rhetorical question that I frequently ask myself. What is worth doing and spending a portion of the unknown amount of time that I have left? How do I decide what's worth the effort? And now YOU can have part of this self dialog in DIGITAL TRADING CARD form! Neat! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool)
